                  "pageId": 233475,
                  "revisionId": 2663923,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "The cost of abilities or their drains can not be less than 25% of their original value. Because of this, Ability Efficiency has an indirect cap of +75%."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Fleeting Expertise",
                  "pageId": 233475,
                  "revisionId": 2663923,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "This means that if combined with a maxed Streamline , any Fleeting Expertise rank above four lowers overall duration without increasing efficiency."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Fleeting Expertise",
                  "pageId": 233475,
                  "revisionId": 2663923,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "If your total Duration is below 100%, the excess efficiency above 175% will still count towards abilities that drain energy over time."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Fleeting Expertise",
                  "pageId": 233475,
                  "revisionId": 2663923,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Efficiency is capped at +75%, however the cap is applied to the result; Therefore efficiency used to compute drain is not capped, although drain is capped."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Fleeting Expertise",
                  "pageId": 233475,
                  "revisionId": 2663923,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Abilities that drain energy over time (such as Immolation or Peacemaker ) will have varying benefits from this mod depending on the amount of Duration Mods you equip."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Fleeting Expertise",
                  "pageId": 233475,
                  "revisionId": 2663923,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Duration mods on these abilities affect the actual length of one second of energy drain."
                }
              }
